'''James Ryan R. Sena''' (born August 31, 1988 in [[Agoo, La Union]]) is a Filipino professional basketball player for the [[Blackwater Elite]] in the [[Philippine Basketball Association]] (PBA). Sena played collegiate basketball at [[Jose Rizal University|JRU]] [[JRU Heavy Bombers|Heavy Bombers]].
