'''Novia Indriani Mamuaja''' (born November 9, 1994) is an [[Indonesia]]n beauty pageant titleholder. She was crowned 3rd Runner-up <ref>[http://missosology.org/more/uncategorized/item/1731-puteri-indonesia-2012-2013-live-updates Whulandary Herman is Puteri Indonesia 2012-2013]</ref> at [[Puteri Indonesia 2013]] and represented her country at Miss Grand International 2013

==Life==
Novia Mamuaja was born in [[Manado]], [[North Sulawesi]], and studied at SMA Katolik Rex Mundi Manado. She joined the national flag-hoisting team (Paskibraka) 2011. Mamuaja had success in local pageants: she was crowned Miss SMP Don Bosco Manado 2009, Putri SMA Rex Mundi Manado 2010, Nona Manado 2012 and Nona Fotogenic 2012. She was 1st Runner-up at Noni Manado 2012.

==Career==
===Puteri Indonesia 2012-2013===
Mamuja competed as the representative of [[North Sulawesi]]. She was crowned 3rd Runner Up at [[Puteri Indonesia 2013]].<ref>[http://kattera.wordpress.com/tag/novia-indriani-mamuaja/ Puteri Indonesia 2013 Result]</ref><ref>[http://indopageants.blogspot.com/2013/01/puteri-indonesia-2012-2013-its-me-its_24.html Official Novia Mamuja]</ref>

===Miss Grand International 2013===
In 2013, the [[Puteri Indonesia|Puteri Indonesia Organization]] sent a representative to Miss Grand International 2013 for the first time ever.<ref>[https://www.facebook.com/pages/Puteri-Indonesia/126595050626?ref=ts&fref=ts Indonesia will debut at the Miss Grand International 2013]</ref>

